d4b3d471-a7d2-47e5-a50c-c99591b24d4e.do_description: To make the output, you have to...copy the entire small square grid without change in  the pattern or the colors along with the border.
d4b3d471-a7d2-47e5-a50c-c99591b24d4e.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the small square inside the input grid.
d4b3d471-a7d2-47e5-a50c-c99591b24d4e.see_description: In the input, you should see...a a small square inside the input grid with border.

d634f3d7-28f6-4ad8-9a3d-c4f4e507a3cc.do_description: To make the output, you have to... count the number of squares in the colored border and resize the output to that number. Then you color all the blocks to match the input.

d634f3d7-28f6-4ad8-9a3d-c4f4e507a3cc.see_description: In the input, you should see....one section that has a different color border
